Troy Britain has joined the Panda's Thumb crew. Troy is a long-time veteran of the creationism wars. He blogs at <a href="http://pigeonchess.com/">Playing Chess with Pigeons</a>. He is a <a href="http://pigeonchess.com/">TalkOrigins Archive</a> volunteer, was a co-founder of the <a href="http://www.antievolution.org/projects/mclean/new_site/index.htm">McLean <i>v.</i> Arkansas Documentation Project</a>, and is a member of both <a href="http://ncse.com/">NCSE</a> and the <a href="http://www.skeptic.com/">Skeptics Society</a>.

Welcome, Troy! We look forward to your posts.
